page.title: 13Henry Loewendahl's Hobbies
page.content: On Monday I usually go and call for my friend Ben.On nice days we usually go in the river or play football and rounders.On Tuesday I do the same sort of things.On Wednesday I go to Judo in Woodstock. I go at 6:30pm,it finishes at 8:30pm.I am an orange belt.I have won 3 trophies.The biggest one is about 30cm tall,it's base is marble.On Thursday's I sometimes cycle to Wootton with Ben.On Fridays I sometimes go swimming at Kidlington pool.On Saturdays the whole family go into Oxford to shop.On Sunday I sometimes go to my camp,and occasionally I go to church.
